Search Physician Office Visit Costs Data sets by Specialty

Source: R/search_datasets.R
search_datasets.Rd

Returns information pertaining to 83 datasets separated by medical specialty, describing physician office visit costs per zip code for new and established patients.

Usage

search_datasets(specialty = NULL, keyword = NULL)

Source

Physician Office Visit Costs (Data.CMS.gov)

Arguments

specialty

search for exact medical specialty, e.g. 'cardiology'

keyword

search for partial matches, e.g. 'medicine'

Value

A tidytable containing the specialty of the provider, the title of the dataset, the dates that the dataset was issued, modified, and released, and the link to download the csv file
